item.description:
The NHLA will host an open "legislative strategy" meeting on September 20th, open to all members. The purpose of the meeting is to discuss bills that members would like to see brought forward, and to coordinate strategies for getting those bills passed. If there's a law that bothers you, don't just complain about it -- come work with us to help get it reformed or repealed!

The meeting will be held at Murphy's Taproom from 11 AM till 3 PM.
item.name: NHLA: Legislative Strategy Session
